'''塔那河紅疣猴'''（[[学名|学名]]：''{{lang|la|Piliocolobus rufomitratus}}''）<ref name=msw3>{{MSW3 Groves | pages = 170}}</ref>，又名'''塔納疣猴'''，是近[[肯雅|肯雅]]東南部[[塔納河|塔納河]][[長廊林|長廊林]]中特有的一種[[瀕危|瀕危]][[猴子|猴子]]。牠們以往被分類為[[西方紅疣猴|西方紅疣猴]]的[[亞種|亞種]]。<ref>{{Cite book en|author=Kingdon, J.|year=1997|title=The Kingdon Guide to African Mammals|url=https://archive.org/details/kingdonfieldguid00jona|publisher=Academic Press Limited|location=London|id=ISBN 0-12-408355-2}}</ref>

塔那河紅疣猴是[[世界|世界]]上最瀕危的25種[[靈長類|靈長類]]之一。<ref>{{Cite book en|author=Butynski, T. M.|year=2005|url=http://www.primate-sg.org/rufomitratus.htm|chapter=Tana River Red Colobus, ''Procolobus rufomitratus'' (Peters, 1879)|title=Primates in Peril: The World's 25 Most Endangered Primates 2004-2006|editor=R. A. Mittermeier, C. Valladares-Pádua, A. B. Rylands, A. A. Eudey, T. M. Butynski, J. U. Ganzhorn, R. Kormos, J. M. Aguiar and S. Walker (eds.)|pages=17|publisher=Report to IUCN/SSC Primate Specialist Group (PSG), International Primatological Society (IPS) and Conservation International (CI)|location=Washington, DC|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110723171907/http://www.primate-sg.org/rufomitratus.htm|archivedate=2011-07-23}}</ref>牠們與[[塔那河長尾猴|塔那河長尾猴]]是1978年在塔納河成立保護區的原因<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.kws.org/tana-river.html|title=Tana River National Primate Reserve|author=Kenya WildLife Service|accessdate=2008-07-20|archive-date=2008-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081007053408/http://www.kws.org/tana-river.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，但在此區內仍受有[[人類|人類]]的騷擾。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.africanconservation.org/content/view/685/405/|title=Kenya's rare monkey species threatened with extinction|author=African Conservation Foundation|accessdate=2008-07-20|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081012100038/http://www.africanconservation.org/content/view/685/405/|archivedate=2008-10-12}}</ref>

